text: Rare resale opportunity in the coveted waterfront condo complex, The Sands. This sun-drenched unit radiates PNW charm & the spot on details of the recent renovation will delight even the most discerning buyer. Enjoy the sweeping west facing saltwater views from your private deck or while strolling the walking path along Birch Bay Drive. The nearly indestructible LVP flooring, new quartz counters, on-trend white cabinets, tile wall & island backsplash & custom stainless steel finishes in the kitchen create a light & bright vibe that seamlessly connects to the living, dining & outdoor spaces. Bonus: in-unit washer & dryer! Nestled between Vancouver, BC & Seattle, WA...Birch Bay is a gem...this is Pacific Northwest living at its finest!

Well maintained park model w/add-a-room w/ wood burning stove. Fully furnished w/2 pullout couches and flat screen TV;s for your guests. This lot get's both sun and shade making it comfortable year round. Fully fenced with a patio and fire pit. The closed Gazebo also has wood burning stove. Tool shed has all you need including a new freezer and two bikes. This gatedCommunity's amenities include 2 pools, Parks, Playgrounds, disc golf, tennis, Nooksack River access, 24/7 security and more.Limited to 120 days/year occupancy, No rentals.

Welcome home to your Vintage original! Own a piece of Glacier history, this is a one owner, first time on the market little rustic GEM located in the sought after Snowline Community! This 2 bedrooms with a very roomy loft, is ready for your personal touches! New beautiful deck to enjoy the outdoors! Some of the amenities include gated entry, outdoor pool, tennis courts, fishing pond, playground, walking trails, community clubhouse & for year round recreation. Currently a part time vacation rental, the opportunity exists to continue using the home as an income earning property. New H2O tank, new metal roof, new deck built for your hot tub. Your own cozy place to make memories! 20 mins to Mt. Baker, and 15 to Silver Lake!

Birch Bay area storage condo! 19' x 48' insulated & heated unit has a 14' x 14' insulated overhead door. Ceiling-mounted natural gas furnace with thermostat. Bright LED lighting! 70 amp electrical panel, with outlets including an RV outlet, and outlets high on back wall for potential future mezzanine. Plenty of room to store most RVs, boats, vehicles, and more! Unit has a monitored fire alarm system. Plans are available for you to add a future mezzanine. Security fencing around complex, with password-controlled automatic gate, and exterior security lighting. 52' drive aisles between buildings. Low maintenance exteriors! This unit is like new!

Lots of great space in this bright home! Easily converted into 2 separate units with a 2 bedroom suite plus a 1 bedroom suite. Recent updates including flooring, drywall, doors, paint. Deck on the rear was removed and is an easy add on. Huge south facing rear yard with tons of sun all day long with manicured lawn, fruit trees, shrubs and flowers. Short walking distance to amenities including parks, the beach, community center, restaurants, post office, groceries and marina. Owner is moving to Europe and there is some minor finishing to complete and this solid home is ready for your personal touches. Purchase price includes all of the furniture, kitchen stuff, new appliances & a new ride on mower! Great location, opportunity, value & price!

Living at 5 Huckleberry Ct feels like having your own private retreat amidst nature. Surrounded by trees and with abundant windows, you can watch the seasons change from every room, feeling like youre in a snow globe in winter or a lush forest in summer. The home combines rustic charm with modern comforts, featuring smart appliances, brand-new LVP floors, all-new lighting, roof, and insulation. Its location offers the best of both worlds: peaceful seclusion near Lookout Mountain and Lake Whatcom, yet just a short drive from downtown Bellinghams amenities. Its a sanctuary where every day feels like a cozy escape.

The most adorable Columbia neighborhood bungalow is here! Tastefully updated in all the right places. A stylish entry opens to character fir floors that exude the Craftsman charm we all love. Curl up in front of the gas fireplace or cook in the updated kitchen featuring new butcher block countertops & gas range, Fisher & Paykel SS fridge + new subway tile backsplash. Two awesome built-in bookcases + window seat & built-in dining area invite a fun social atmosphere. A charming guest bedroom + lg full bath line the hallway. W/D in '22. The oversized main bedroom offers vaulted ceilings, major closet space & warm bamboo floors. Access the fenced, private back yard w/ a killer bike/shop space w/ power. Best eats, brews, trails, schools + more!

Rare opportunity to enjoy life in one of the most desirable areas of Lake Whatcom! Situated on 125 ft of waterfront in sought-after Strawberry Point, this property offers all-day sun, stunning views & incredible privacy. Luxurious main-level primary suite w/ a fireplace & cedar sauna. Seamless integration of indoor/outdoor spaces & amenities including a covered heated patio, in-ground hot tub, & built-in gas fire pit & BBQthe ideal place to relax & entertain. Wine fridge & new Bertazzoni appliances in the kitchen. Detached ADU (an add'l 636 sq ft) offers versatile living options. Recently restored dock is protected by a natural jetty. Nothing to do but launch your boat; this well-loved home is ready to make new memories to last a lifetime!

Welcome to this charming main-level condo! Tucked away in a serene setting on Bellingham's southside, this condo offers the perfect blend of privacy and convenience. Two bedrooms and a versatile den/office are ideal for working from home. The open floor plan boasts plenty of windows that fill the space w/ natural light. Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the main room. Spacious primary suite features an ensuite bathroom, two closets, one a walk-in. The stylish kitchen offers ample storage & counter space, incl all appliances. Enjoy the benefits of two full baths and an attached one-car garage with extra storage. You're just steps away from the Interurban Trail, providing easy access to Fairhaven, Downtown Bellingham, parks, the waterfront.

Priced to sell! Great lot in Gate 13, ULID has been paid on lot 55. A lovely and private lot to build your next home, this could be the one!. All Sudden valley amenities include golf course, marina, hiking trails, swimming pool, tennis courts, beaches, boat launch and 24/7 security.

Imagine coming home to gorgeous, freshly updated interior design, & stunning, green fairway views! This spacious 4BR, 2.5BA dream home has been fully remodeled with thoughtful layout & quality finishes. New vinyl plank floors throughout, tongue & groove ceilings w/exposed beams, + stainless steel appliances create a luxury feel on your main level. Your upstairs features a huge primary suite w/vaulted ceilings/loft with storage space, picture windows, slider to balcony, & even a closet/office + kitchenette for a possible MIL space! Enjoy entertaining in the lower level media rm w/separate entrance, or hosting out on the fabulous deck. Excellent gate 1 location near golf course, marina, trails & more make this a cant-miss property!

Welcome to a stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath, and an office home in one of Ferndale's most desirable neighborhoods. This 2, 430 sq ft residence, built in 2022, boasts top-of-the-line finishes throughout. The gourmet kitchen features high-end appliances and ample storage, perfect for entertaining, don't miss the prep kitchen as well! The spacious living area includes a cozy fireplace. The Primary suite offers his and hers walk-in closets and luxurious en-suite bathroom. Enjoy outdoor living with a wood porch and balcony. Located in the desirable Heather Ridge subdivision, this home combines elegance with modern amenities. Peekaboo views of mountains from the top floor top off this amazing build, come see for yourself today

Discover your secluded sanctuary in this 4 bed, 2 bath home. Embrace the spacious primary bedroom with a walk-in closet, alongside three other generously sized rooms, each featuring its own walk-in closet. Recently renovated with updated appliances, plumbing, fixtures, flooring, tile backsplash, and concrete countertops, this home exudes modern comfort. Stay cozy with a pellet stove and enjoy peace of mind with a new roof installed in 2020. Located in RR Ranch, residents enjoy amenities such as a large swimming pool, horse arena, picnic shelter, and play area. Only moments away from Birch Bay's beaches and recreational activities, this home is perfect for entertaining with ample space for a boat/RV and outdoor enjoyment.

Park like 20 acre parcel with multiple building sites zoned R10A with 2 Meadowdale water shares for possible future division. The property is mostly treed with cedar and has 15, 800 board feet of high-quality cedar ready for sale or use. The property fronts on Badger Rd for easy access to power and water. It has been used as a family recreation site for 30+years, but would make a serene, secluded building site!

One of Lynden's most desired 55+ condo communities, Ridgeview Creek! Open floor plan provides an abundance of natural daylight. Vaulted ceilings, radiant heat, gas fireplace, custom built-ins, deluxe master bath with soaker tub, French doors, granite in the gourmet kitchen, and no steps anywhere! New carpet and interior paint, Levelor window coverings, and built in lighted display cabinet recently added and updated. Includes two car garage, spacious patio, and private yard with creek view. HOA attends to maintenance and landscaping for carefree living! Walking distance to restaurants, shopping, and more. Don't miss this opportunity to be a part of the picturesque and friendly Lynden community!

Sprawling 3.37acre move in ready park like estate only minutes to Blaine! Rambler boasts 2, 288 sq.ft. of move in ready living space. Covered front carport entry leads to vaulted great room w/ chef's kitchen & dining area. Living room w/ brick fireplace & wood stove. Large windows & lots of natural light throughout. Primary suite w/ fully updated en suite inc tile shower & soaking tub. Second bedroom w/ 3/4 bath attached. 3rd bedroom or office. Massive laundry room. Attached 2 car garage. Outside find 40'x70' shop w/ 6 bays including drivethru RV doors & so much space for all your hobbies & toys! Heat pump, furnace & roof in 2015. Level & dry acreage w/ lots of usable space. This property has everything you are looking for!

Pristine custom Craftsman home designed for entertaining & aging-in-place. The home is situated on one of the most desireable lots on Semiahmoo Golf Course, due to its prime location at the end of a cul-de-sac with over 300' of golf course frontage along two sides of the 1/3+ acre lot. View of the 9th green & pond from the back patio. Directly access the first tee box, clubhouse, pool & sport courts! Low-maintenance perennial gardens. No detail overlooked in the thoughtful floor plan. All primary living spaces are on the main level, plus 1000+ sqft upstairs: Bonus room, office/gym, wet bar, 200+ bottle climate-controlled wine closet and storage room. Tall, elegant coffered ceilings with accent lighting, wide hallways and 36 wide doorways.

Rare Snowline lot in very private area with a short walk to amenities & trails. Phone, power, & water in the street. Enjoy all that Mt. Baker has to offer with year round fun at a second home or a new lifestyle. Ski, snowboard, kayak, hike, mountain bike, fish or just relax. Nooksack River is a short walk away via access trail. Snowline amenities include sport courts, pool, clubhouse, ball field, trails, playground & pond. Previous owner had an expired septic design but no current permit. This lot is boasting in potential to be the perfect mountain get away.

Perfect opportunity to purchase and build your dream home with sweeping harbor and mountain views. Fully serviced site with all utilities and high speed interenet in the street. The almost half acre lot is just waiting for your ideas to build your special home that captures all the view - just minutes from the US/Canadian border and mere steps away from miles of walking trails, golf course, boating, and many more PNW activities that the Semiahmoo Resort community offers. You'll never need to go oin vacation when you can just live and work in this magical place. Design guidelines are easy to follow and protect long term values--use the builder of your choice and move in to a new home in 2024!

One-of-a-kind acreage gem in city limits! This meticulously maintained, 3-bed, 1.75-bath, farm-style home sits on nearly 5 beautiful acres. Inside the home boasts eye catching oak floors, a versatile dining room, natural light throughout and countless unique features. Outside you'll discover multiple fenced-in areas, RV pad with hookups, a gated entrance, and a creek! It doesn't stop there, with a barn, a fully functional shop enhanced with a 1/2 bath, and endless storage areas, the usage is unlimited. Quietly nestled on a dead-end street, the home offers unparalleled privacy and feels like country living with benefits of all in-city amenities. This epic property is a rare find for those seeking a private oasis to enjoy for years to come.

High quality Moduline MF home with open floor plan. Inviting living room that flows into dining area that features a vaulted ceiling. Master Suite with 3/4 bath and cedar lined closet. 2nd bedroom sits next to a full bathroom. Utility room with water and dryer, storage unit in tandem carport and full length gate trex deck that surrounds the front of the home. Additional bonus storage space under the unit with access. Upgraded blinds, 2015 Heat Pump for A/C, vinyl laminate flooring and kitchen w/ eating bar... must see home!

Welcome to this beautifully updated home featuring 3 bedrooms plus a versatile den, perfect for home office, playroom, or guests. This charming residence offers a spacious layout with ample natural light & modern finishes. The primary suite boasts a luxurious ensuite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are generously sized & share a well-appointed bathroom. The den provides extra space to meet your needs, whether for work or leisure. Enjoy the open-concept living area that seamlessly connects to the contemporary kitchen, ideal for entertaining. The private backyard & convenient location complete this wonderful home. Low Space rent of $550 includes W/S. Community park, playground & guest parking. No age restrictions.

The perfect opportunity to own a charming, newly updated one-level home on a nice, quiet street in South Bellingham. Through the front door you will be greeted by a flowing floor plan flooded with natural light. A great room concept with vaulted ceilings adjoins a quality kitchen with beautiful quartz countertops and new appliances. This 3 bed, 2 bath lives large and features a flex bedroom/office with French doors, primary bedroom with ensuite bath and an attached 2 car garage. Enjoy a spacious fenced backyard with a concrete patio off the dining room. Just a short drive to Sehome Village shopping, downtown Bellingham, WWU and easy access to I-5. A great house in a desirable Bellingham location!

Your dream home! Updated, single-level gem boasts spacious living room w/laminate flooring seamlessly flowing into dining area. Kitchen is a chef's delight w/tile backsplash, farmhouse sink & butcher block counters. Bathed in natural light & offering peekaboo views of B'ham Bay, you'll relish the sunsets from your primary suite, complete w/full bath & large closet. 3 generous bedrooms, fully fenced sunny backyard w/storage shed, garden beds, freshly stained deck & concrete patio. An insulated garage w/backyard access, circular driveway, & extra parking add convenience. A stroll away from downtown, Little Squalicum Park, trails, & the soon-to-be renovated Pier extending into B'ham Bay, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort & location

6233 Hamilton hits a lot of buttons, with great floor plan, great yard, great sun exposure, air conditioning. This is a four-bedroom 2.5 baths home with spacious bonus room, used as a 5th bedroom. Main level includes tile entry transitioning to engineered flooring and luxury vinyl flooring, primary with ensuite with walk-in closet, Kitchen open to the Great room with Natural Gas fireplace, separate dining room, utility room with access to the two-car garage. From the Great room there is access to the lengthy patio complete with Gazebo, mature landscaping, water features in the fully fenced backyard garden. Upstairs, 3 bedrooms, one full bath and sizable bonus room use for many different needs.

Discover this charming 4 bed/3 bath home in a prime location, just a short stroll to downtown Blaines shops, dining & waterfront. This open-concept gem features a spacious kitchen with stunning quartz countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and a large walk-in pantry. Stay cool in the summer & warm in the winter with the ductless mini splits. Enjoy the covered deck overlooking a large, fenced yard, complete with a dog run. With RV hookups & ample room to park extra vehicles, this home offers both convenience & comfort. Don't miss out on this exceptional property in a vibrant, walkable neighborhood!

Move-in ready home in Nooksack. Enjoy the convenience of one level living. Three bedroom, one bath home on an 11, 000+ square foot lot. Unwind in your large back yard ready for your garden, fire pit, and pets. New roof in 2023, ductless mini split for heating and cooling. Located out of the flood zone. Plenty of off street parking for an RV. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to get into the market.

Nestled in a sweet cul-de-sac, this stunning home is not to be missed! Every inch of this single-level home has been masterfully crafted, w/Douglas Fir framing, a Presidential roof, Milgard Windows, Quartz windowsills & radiant heat tile flooring. The chef's kitchen features Thermador appliances, Quartz countertops & backsplash, & Wi-fi connect Espresso Machine. A gorgeous ensuite with large soaking tub, walk-out shower, dimmable backlit mirrors and large walk-in closet lends a lavish feel to the primary suite. Enjoy conveniences of central vacuum, security system, on-demand hot water & A/C. The 1.4-acre professionally landscaped & fully-fenced yard leaves plenty of room for a shop/ADU, in addition to the existing 4-car garage. Pure Luxury!

Talk about loving where you live! How about a 3 yr old 4 bd 3.5 bath beauty with seamless open floor plan, top quality kitchen featuring granite c-tops and high end appliances. Features two large primary bdrms with luxurious en suites one on main floor and one on second level AND it sits front row to one of this worlds most enchanting playgrounds, The Salish Sea and San Juan Islands make up your back yard. Walk off your patio, down your ramp to your private dock and you are minutes away. Located in the premier The East Cove (lots of room to maneuver) area of Sandy Point Shores Marina. The live action views from your waterfront marina property along with the pool, golf course and clubhouse this community offers make this a win/win.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District

text: This meticulously maintained property embodies craftsmanship and detail in the scenic Glen at Maple Falls. A trailer with two additional rooms-a large but cozy living room and 2nd bedroom, along with a separate bunkhouse, comfortably accommodates up to 8 guests with 4 double beds. Its pristine condition speaks volumes about the care it has received over the years. New water heater, new toilet, new gravel. Built-in BBQ & mini fridge on the inviting covered front porch & beautiful fully fenced yard area. Turnkey-just enjoy! Zoned recreational for 120 days of use per year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, a hot tub, sports courts, a library, a laundromat, 2 clubhouses, 24-hour security/gated, & playgrounds.

Brand new 2-story home which has just been completed in the lakeside & golf course community of Sudden Valley. this 2-story, 3 bedroom home is located on a flat, corner lot, which is surrounded by 2 vacant lots which have been turned into permanent green-belt by the Sudden Valley community. Lots of 'elbow room' here! Enjoy an open great room with kitchen, dining area & living room on the main level. Easy access to a large, low level deck directly off of the living area. The kitchen has white cabinet package, large island with quartz counter top, & stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom is upstairs & has ensuite bath with large glass enclosed shower & walk-in closet. Room for a small office upstairs as well - or sitting area.

Welcome home to Glenhaven! This charming property offers 3 beds, 3 baths, and 2004 sq ft of comfortable living space. The great room downstairs is perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. Enjoy the convenience of walking trails and the weekly visit of a mobile book bus every Monday. This desirable neighborhood offers a community pool, access to the lakes, parks and more. This home is a true gem!

Endless potential! This home resides in the coveted Edgemoor neighborhood, only minutes from Historic Fairhaven. Three bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, lightly lived in, and personality throughout! Solarium adds that mid-century character that has made a comeback in recent decor. Daylight basement never been finished, ready for your ideas... family room? MIL suite? you name it! Outside entrance makes for unlimited options. Mature landscaping, including Rhododendrons and privacy trees around property - a little hedge trimming and weeding will make this property shine and some elbow grease will give you immediate equity. Don't miss out!

Welcome to this stunning home at 3607 Ridgemont Way in Bellingham, WA! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a finished basement and a perfect blend of comfort and modern living. Featuring an open floor plan the bright and airy living room flows seamlessly into the tastefully updated kitchen. Enjoy cozy evenings by one of two fireplaces or step outside to the landscaped backyard, ideal for entertaining. This home has been tastefully updated from top to bottom with new windows, appliances paint and so much more! Located in a serene neighborhood, youll be minutes away from parks, trails, and shopping. Dont miss this incredible opportunityschedule your private tour today!

The Ivy by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a stunning design you do not want to miss. Upon entry find a soaring Two-Story Foyer a corner set a Home Office. Deeper into the home, the Two-Story Great Room is paired perfectly with a sophisticated Dining room and mutually connected Gourmet Kitchen flush with 3cm Quartz counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry. For even more space, a main floor Multi-Purpose Room is tucked just off the kitchen. Upstairs, look out onto the Great Room from the front-facing Leisure room that leads to three secondary bedrooms and the luxurious Grand Suite. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

This is it - the dream home right next to Lake Padden! This charming 1940s Dutch Colonial home has it all: location, style & charm. Main floor is warm & welcoming: a fantastic classic floor plan with 2 delightful main living areas each with a welcoming wood stove. The recently updated kitchen is bright & beautiful complimenting the character of the home. Upstairs features 2 bedrooms overlooking the beautiful yard & a full bathroom. Life outside is a delight: natural landscaping, private patio w/ fire pit, hot tub, fenced yard & mature trees. Have it all with quiet neighborhood living & daily walks, runs or paddles at Lake Padden park. World class mountain biking at Galbraith, parks and beaches just minutes away. Must see this one in person!

Your majestic valley farmland awaits!Privacy, seclusion, serenity & stunning mountain views!This rare 42+ acre farm spans over 3 parcels & is a canvas for your dreams.Bordering the South Fork of the Nooksack River, once a cattle ranch, still equipped with a 7k+ft Barn housing 5 concrete alleys, feeder row, stall alleys & a center way large enough for a semi.A lovingly well thought out garden & orchard stoked with apple, plum, pear & cherry (3 types)trees, berry verities, rhubarb & lavender are just some of the abundant gifts these fertile grounds offer.The sweet home has an addition with pine vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace & skylights making it live light & bright.Vitality radiates here, make this YOUR land! +SELLER FINANCING NOW AVAILABLE+

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Reservations Only. Prices subject to change. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Beautiful treed lot backing up to hundreds of acres of protected hillside forest. Just West of Galbraith Mountain biking trails. Currently no access or services to the lot, which would make a great holding investment for the future. Buy now and benefit later when this lot is buildable for your forested lot close to world-class mountain biking.

First time home buyer? Investor? Look no further! This two bed, two bath town house is centrally located in the heart of Bellingham just steps away from Rosevelt Park. This unit has great bones and an unbeatable proximity to schools, public transit, shopping & dining. Come see it for yourself!

Step into your contemporary craftsman surrounded by 5 acres of natural beauty! As you enter, the sleek concrete floors, open living/dining space, fireplace, & exposed beams create touch of elegance. Stunning kitchen w/unlimited storage. Primary on main w/walk-in closet, ensuite bath & private. Main floor office/gym opens to yard. Upstairs has flex space + 2 beds/full bath & HUGE bonus room. Outside on the covered patio, soak in the tranquility of deer/eagle sightings & your own stream!. Enjoy the firepit or indulge in the spa like sauna for ultimate relaxation. Located just minutes from the Canadian border & less than 2 hours from Seattle, this residence offers the perfect balance of seclusion and accessibility. Incomparable to find!

This Gate 1 Sudden Valley home is ready for new owners! The level lot abuts to SVCA open space and is located in a terrific cul-de-sac with an amazing backyard that contains a huge deck for entertaining, playing, relaxing and the trees/shrubs give extra privacy. This 4 bedroom home has an attached 2-car garage, newer appliances (kitchen & laundry), instant-hot water, granite counters, kitchen bar, separate laundry, skylights, vaulted ceilings, and updated lighting throughout. The primary suite includes French door entrance, ceiling fan, en-suite bath with double sinks, jetted tub, and separate shower. The Sudden Valley community has a ton to offer with a pool, gym, beaches, marina, golf course, library, and trails.

No stone left unturned on this tastefully updated rambler in the coveted Letter Streets neighborhood! In the heart of Bellingham on a corner lot, fully finished garage, and fully fenced yard, this 2 bed and 1 bath home will not disappoint. Outside you will enjoy a brand new roof and gutters, new porch addition and luscious sod grass in the backyard. Inside has new everything including Quartz countertops in kitchen and bath with custom tile work backsplash and shower, solid wood construction white shaker cabinetry, wide plank LVP flooring throughout, new trim and doors, LED lighting, high end LG stainless appliances, mini-split and wall heaters, fresh paint inside and out. Spacious side yard to play or potential for ADU!

Absolute charm in this 2 bd 1 bath fully remodeled turn-of-the century home on huge over 14, 000 sq ft lot! Beautiful laminate wood flooring throughout, tall ceilings & windows, & completely updated kitchen. Granite, stainless steel appliances, & eat-in bar all open to dining/living room from kitchen. 2 good size bedrooms w/built in closets plus full bathroom complete this well laid out floor plan. Sunny utility room w/newer included washer & dryer leads to huge backyard. Lower patio w/cozy firepit perfect for enjoying summer nights. Alley access to newer shop w/tall ceilings for extra storage. Topped off w/another garden shed & playset - this property & home are ready for new owners!

Epic bay view from this mid-century modern South Hill home. 17th is arguably the quietest street on the hill. Very walkable with easy access to many desirable locations. Great quiet and private back patio for entertaining. This house has had many recent updates and improvements. Solar panels keep power bills very low. Work from your home office with a stunning bay view. Or use as a guest bedroom. The basement has been recently modified as a mother-in-law suite. With its own entrance, the basement could easily be rented for additional income. Many options with this well cared for home.

Beautiful 2 bedroom 1-3/4 bath 1096 sq ft home located in the very desirable over 55 community known as Fieldstone Place. New roof, new carpet, new exterior paint, new SS appliance package & new insulated garage overhead door. Attached 2 car garage with sink. Vaulted ceilings. Walking distance to the community ctr, golf course, fitness club and fine dining. Short distance to downtown,

Introducing The Alder B plan, with 2 car garage on the southwest perimeter of Woodberry's new gated community at Semiahmoo. This plan lives like a one-level home and has 2 bedrooms with office on the main floor including the Primary suite. There are 1.75 baths on the Primary Level. Up you have 2 bedrooms, full bath and loft area. Quality flooring, heat pumps with heating, and air conditioning. Soft close cabinets, quartz countertops, nice lighting package, island in the kitchen. Heated floors in the Primary and so much more. Come see the model home now open. Area amenities, Golf Marina, Tennis club, Ornithologist dream, walking trails kayaking, biking. Sage Homes Northwest Site Registration No. 4908.

Discover the perfect blend of comfort and nature in this well maintained & financeable 1991 double-wide manufactured home. Nestled in a tranquil and sunny location at the end of a private road this home backs onto forested acreage and faces a grassy open space. This delightful home with bamboo floors throughout offers 2 spacious beds, 2 baths, a versatile den & a cozy fireplace in an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The 9000 sq. ft. lot is a gardeners delight. The covered back deck affords a relaxing view over the expansive yard with fruit trees, blueberries & established shrubs. There's a shed for storage & an additional bunkie/office with power and water Some rooms are virtually staged 55+ Community

Discover this well-maintained south side 1 bedroom condo at Cypress Place, boasting high-end upgrades & modern amenities. Enjoy smart appliances and ample cabinet space in the kitchen, along with a large full bath featuring great storage and in-unit laundry for ultimate convenience. The spacious living room doubles as a versatile workspace, while the separate bedroom offers additional space & privacy. Step onto the green tree lined patio and relish in the Pacific Northwest charm. Added perks include secured lobby entry, building elevator, assigned parking, secure bike storage, and access to the fitness center. With a prime location near I-5, WWU, and shopping, this unit offers low-maintenance living without sacrificing space or convenience.

Unlock the true potential of this early 1900s Craftsman, conveniently nestled in the heart of Sunnyland. Moments away from Trader Joes, restaurants, and more. This quaint residence is a blank canvas, awaiting the touch to make it yours. Home features a spacious living and dining area with tall ceilings. Both bedrooms are complete with en suite bathrooms, complemented by an additional full bath off the kitchen. Detached two-car garage features a finished 400-square-foot studio space, equipped with a kitchenette and full bathideal for guests, a home office, or potential rental income. If you've been waiting for the perfect opportunity to make your mark with sweat equity on a charming home in a desirable neighborhood, this is the one!

Nestled in Ferndale's Pacific Highland neighborhood, this charming 4 bed, 2.5 bath, 2, 808 sqft home provides comfort and warmth. The living room, anchored by a cozy fireplace, invites relaxation and gatherings, while the adjacent dining room provides a perfect setting for shared meals. The kitchen, equipped with SS appliances and a breakfast nook, offers both functionality and style. On the upper level, 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms provide ample space for rest and privacy, with the primary bedroom and an en-suite bathroom. Outside, the backyard and covered deck offer a serene retreat, while the home's proximity to schools, parks and tennis court ensures convenience and desirable locality.

Relax the days away in your very own piece of heaven in The Glen at Maple Falls with this very well located recreational property. Backing up to green space and a trail to the Nooksack River, this private and well maintained 2012 park model with covered porch has all the amenities to make this your home away from home. The gazebo boasts a queen bed, while another bunkhouse provides two more sleeping spaces, perfect for friends. Shed space for extra storage rounds out this amazing property. Neighboring property is also for sale (MLS 2254695), partner with friends or buy both for added privacy, room for guests, and more. The Glen has 24/7 security, 2 pools (one year-round!), hot tub, clubhouses, sports courts and more!

This gorgeous straw bale home has a unique beauty & feel with its soft curves, 10' wood & beam ceilings, deep window wells & R-48 insulating factor. Walk into its warm, organic style that wraps you in a feeling of peace and tranquility. Special features include a beach rock fireplace, guest wing w/ private bath, a 2nd floor bonus room (plus art closet), lovely gardens & a studio above the 2 car garage. Nice indoor-outdoor flow with Fr. doors leading to private, covered deck. This lovely home is in a fantastic location, just a short walk to the beach, easy walk to the library, store and post office. Here is a great opportunity for those that work from home, artists or those that want a shared or multi-generational layout.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School, Ferndale School District

text: This is more than just a condo; it's a lifestyle! This freshly painted loft condo offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings and an open floorplan with large windows overlooking the 18th fairway. The home features a vintage freestanding fireplace, two full bathrooms and spacious primary bedroom. What truly sets this home apart is its prime location and the array of amenities just steps away from your door. Enjoy the 18-hole golf course, marina and boat storage, private beaches, outdoor pool, fitness center, coffee shop, tennis and basketball courts, and miles of scenic trails for all of your outdoor adventures. Short term rentals allowed with 30-day minimum.

Located just outside of the city limits, this home in Woodbine Estates is ready for you. New roof last year, new exterior paint, new windows in bedrooms, new carpet in bedrooms, new furnace in '18. The flow between the living area, kitchen, and dining room is spacious. Lots of cabinet space in the kitchen. The new KitchenAid stove in the center island is a bonus! All appliances stay including the freezer in the garage. Large front yard and in the back, enjoy the park like setting with plenty of privacy on the back deck. Open the gate in the back yard for access to the trail system. Bike to Lake Padden, Whatcom Falls Park, or Galbraith! Plenty of room to park RV on side of driveway. Located close to town for convenience! Come see this gem!

Experience the best of South Side living in this second-floor corner unit, conveniently level with the parking area. Enjoy panoramic Bay, mountain & island views. This condo features 2 bedrooms, an office & two full baths & has hardwood floors, new carpet & fresh paint. Offers unobstructed views & the location is unbeatable. Strategically positioned between the vibrant Fairhaven district & downtown, it overlooks Boulevard Park & the Boardwalk, offering quick access to waterfront paths. The condo is also near numerous trails, parks & shopping. You'll be within walking distance of boutiques & restaurants in Fairhaven, as well as cultural & recreational activities downtown. Everything you need is just a short stroll or bike ride away!

Discover your dream home in desirable Edgemoor neighborhood! This stunning single-level home was fully updated in 2012 & has been meticulously maintained since. Home boasts beautiful kitchen w/ elegant cherry wood cabinets & kitchen island, perfect for entertaining. The home features oak hardwood & slate floors, complemented by cozy gas fireplace w/ slate surround. Enjoy year-round comfort in the Four Seasons sunroom, w/ heated slate floor, providing a serene space to relax. The house is equipped w/ A/C & generator, ensuring comfort & convenience year round. Enjoy time on the spacious front deck or on the patio in the fenced backyard, ideal for outdoor gatherings. Property includes a custom-designed garden shed & tons of gardening space!

Discover serenity in this charming 3 bed, 1 bath Alabama Hill home on a large sunny lot. Updated with a newer roof, gutters, and vinyl windows for efficiency and comfort. Ductless Mini split for economical heating and cooling. Enormous fully fenced backyard includes a concrete patio, apple and plum trees, blueberry bushes and planter boxes. Large driveway + tons of off-street parking. Steps away from St. Claire Park and the Whatcom Falls Park trailhead, and minutes to all the amenities Bellingham has to offer.

Investment Opportunity Special! This old Bellingham bungalow sits between multi-family buildings, is rented for $900 per month, and is a perfect multi build site. Offered on reasonable seller terms. Collect rent while your plans get approved. Current zoning is RM2L5 soon to change to Middle Housing zoning. Within a stone's throw of the City's offices on Pacific Street. Has alley access, part fenced, and priced to sell!

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Padden model has all the living on main floor that extends out through modern French doors onto a large covered patio. Private backyard with 6' fence, gate, modern pavers, low maintenance turf and raised bed planters and a corner lot. Upstairs you'll find the primary with attached ensuite and 2 more bedrooms with connected bath. Don't forget the detached flex space with half bath and separate entrance that can be used as an office, family room, or for guests.

Amazing Home with Buyer Bonus for fighting the terrible rates, this forever home is Nestled in serene PNW forest on a 4.57-acre property, minutes from town, this newly constructed modern home boasts an impressive 3090 sqft of contemporary living space. Expansive windows throughout the home frame picturesque views of the lush forest. The open-concept living area features vaulted ceilings, white oak engineered h/wd floors, and a stunning double sided fireplace. Gourmet kitchen, where top of the line appliances, waterfall edge island, and a large walk in pantry create an ideal environment for culinary creativity. Two laundry rooms provide added convenience. 3 bedrooms and an extra finished room/nursery/gym upstairs. Buy with confidence!
Cash only fixer on a nice big flat lot. Enjoy all the GlenHaven amenities. All personal items will be removed before closing. House being sold as is. Recent passing septic inspection.

Step into your new sanctuary - a contemporary 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom manufactured home that embodies modern living. Nestled in a serene park setting, this property harmonizes comfort and style, creating an airy, welcoming ambiance from the moment you walk through the door. The spacious, well-lit living area seamlessly flows into the open kitchen, where stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and microwave, elevate both form and function. With its sleek design and abundant natural light, this kitchen is not just a culinary space but a statement of refined living. Additionally, the utility room offers convenient access to the back area through a rear door. Welcome to your new haven.

A storybook home w/ a stunning interior. This is a must-tour for everyone in the price range. Across the street from a beautiful city-owned greenbelt wrought with forestry, bike trails, and Sunset Pond, this location allows for easy access to all of Bellingham on foot, vehicle, bike, and transit. Enjoy a unique craftsman charm born of one-of-a-kind architecture. The main level of this 2016 home was once a 1924 bungalow in Bellingham's Broadway Park. Completely modernized systems complement the preservation of its original craftsman interior. 100 yr oak floors and remarkable trim/molding will wow you from the onset. Lower level is all new from 2016. String lights abound on your back patio where you'll gather & garden in crisp landscaping.

Outstanding opportunity for multi-generational living at this delightful sought after Bob Hall Road location...2, 070 sq ft 3 bedroom/2 bathroom main house + second stand alone building with 750 sq ft guest quarters. The main house features a light & bright open concept kitchen/living/dining design with updated quartz counters & LVP flooring. The versatile outbuilding has ADU potential with 1 bedroom/1 bathroom, full kitchen, living room + 2 car attached garage. Don't miss the incredible sunrise and sunsets or the covered outdoor relaxing/entertaining area. This 1.2 acre mountain view estate is ideal for the buyer looking for privacy or for loads of space for boat/RV parking. Bonus: Lynden School District + Xfinity is available here!

Hard to find 4 bdrm almost 2, 000 sq ft home in nice condition. Easy access Sudden Valley home located on peaceful 1 way street. Spacious bright & open featuring vaulted ceilings, In floor radiant heat, Thru kitchen w/breakfast bar & great room feel to dining & living room w/gas fireplace. Sliding door access to tree lined privacy yard & deck. Just updated w/ new carpet, LVP flooring, interior paint, Kitchen sink & new refrigerator. Multi purpose lower level w/family room & coveted spacious 4th bdrm w/slider door access to private patio - ideal for home office, exercise room, or ??. Nice sized utility room & Extra large garage. Short walk to Huckelberry park. SV amenities Nearby: golf course, marina, beach, 24/7 security, pool and tennis.

Indulge in the awe-inspiring, unobstructed views of the Bay and Islands from this exquisite residence. Impeccably designed home offers an unparalleled sense of refined luxury and comfort. The living room seamlessly flows onto a spacious deck, where the panoramic vistas become an extension of your living space, perfect for entertaining or unwinding. Well-appointed kitchen is a culinary delight. Primary, a spa-like ensuite offers a peaceful escape. Generously scaled rooms provide ample space for relaxation and productivity, while the library is a retreat for literary escapes. Meticulously landscaped grounds, access to outdoor recreation and in proximity to urban conveniences, this home epitomizes a blend of upscale living and natural beauty.

Just 1 BLOCK from WWU's beautiful campus & with MILLION DOLLAR VIEWS of the Bay, Islands & City! This 2-spacious-bedroom 1-full-bath condo is a perfect alternative to renting or dorm living. All-electric, easy to own & maintain, 7 steps up from sidewalk-level & ideally located. Enjoy home-cooked meals in the open kitchen then take it out to the view balcony for Bellingham Bay's World Class Sunsets! Features in-unit laundry w/washer/dryer included. Designated off-street parking spot + street parking. Seconds to WWU, minutes to downtown, affordable investment w/no rental cap! Take advantage of Bellingham's appreciating property values then sell when you're done! Wealth-building-and-preservation 101 at 729 High St. #203.

Excellent opportunity to purchase a vacant lot close to town, with views of the Bay and mountains AND ability to proceed with a home construction with septic and building permits already completed. The owners of this property have spent over 2 years with all the technical data required with the county in getting the home ready to start construction and their immediate plans then changed and they are unable to proceed. Thus, the septic permit has been approved and all of the building plans for a home have been approved by the county and now all needed is to take over and start. The construction company has indicated they still can get this project scheduled in immediately to break ground if you wanted to still us them (but not required).

Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the popular east side of Lynden! This stunning 2, 029 square foot, 2-story residence offers 3 bedrooms, a den w/elegant French doors, & 2.5 baths. The property boasts a 7, 405 square foot lot, featuring a fully fenced backyard complete with extended patio & charming gazebo, ideal for outdoor gatherings. The garden shed provides additional storage for your gardening tools. Vaulted ceilings in the gathering room create an open airy feel, along with a cozy gas fireplace. The kitchen is outfitted with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, & bar seating. Enjoy the convenience of a spacious main floor primary bedroom, providing a serene retreat with easy access. Dont miss this opportunity!

This architecturally designed and custom built Whistler-style NW craftsman home is very unique and privately situated on over 10 acres (2 parcel #'s), surrounded by evergreens overlooking a pond and a stream. The details of this home are incredible with main floor living, wood timbers and beams, dramatic entry, open floor plan, generously sized rooms, wood-lined vaulted ceilings, floor-to-ceiling south facing windows for passive solar heating, wrap-around deck with covered outdoor kitchen, new high-efficiency furnace and heat pump, new on-demand hot water tank, mini kitchen set up for an ADU in the basement, and a 40 x 48 shop with covered wood storage. This estate is located just 15 minutes from Bellingham and it is so tranquil and serene.

Live in this stunning waterfront home with views of BOTH Drayton Harbor and the ocean (includes Mt. Baker and SE to SW panoramic unobstructed - one of only two sites!). Private gated entry with direct access to miles of trails and beaches. This unit also has a huge patio and landscaped yard (over 11, 000 sq ft total). The attention to detail, soaring ceilings and high-end finishes make this unit arguably one of the best. Butler pantry off kitchen, wine fridge, high-end appliances throughout, also has a bonus living space with stunning views above the garage - do not miss any details - call for a private tour!

Come see this spectacular Lake Whatcom view lot with the incredible building site already cleared. No guesswork on this lot of what your view will be. Build your dream home on this incredible lot that gets all day sun. Owner has approved plans available or design your own dream home. You can see Stewart Mt, Galbraith Mt, and Sudden Valley from this site. You feel like you are miles away from civilization but you're only 10 mins to Barkley Village. Keep the world close with fiber optics. Enjoy the community walking trail around the project while the gated access gives peace of mind. The abundant wildlife gives the nature lover constant viewing possibilities. Don't miss the opportunity to see this estate property.

Charming turn of the century craftsman home located in the heart of Lynden within walking distance to schools, shopping, dining and bus lines! Bring your ideas and vision to this home with tons of potential. 3 beds upstairs and 2 down for a total of 5 beds & 1 bath w/ extra office or living/flex space on the main level. Potentially add a bathroom and convert this space to a main level primary bedroom in a remodel. Solid wood floors have the potential of being refinished to bring the original beauty back. A good opportunity to move in now and renovate over time for equity building in a great Lynden location. Vacant, view anytime.

Newly updated bungalow with lower-level studio in the heart of Lynden. Step into this charming home that has been recently renovated to perfection, and discover a thoughtfully designed interior flooded with natural light. The kitchen has the sweetest disposition featuring butcher block countertops, painted cabinets, and a gas range with a decorative plaster hood vent. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area opens to a patio, creating the perfect setting for al fresco dining.The lower level studio is complete with its own entrance, bathroom, and kitchenette. Other updates include, new windows, doors, flooring, lighting and roof! Every detail of this home has been carefully considered resulting in a curated and functional living space.
